HEADWORD: Pettitoes
<hw>Pet"ti*toes</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Petty</ets> + <ets>toes</ets>.]</ety> <def>The toes or feet
